{"tid":605782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"增加土地供應無用　自由港　無資本管制　熱錢入　樓價升　撤就冧　郊野維港　高場棕地　白犧牲","createTime":"2018-03-26T03:30:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T16:01:40.000Z","uid":47714,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1f669245ad70775d682e95593e6272c51dc68a92","tid":605782,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T03:30:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/977429739433373696\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F977429739433373696&d=O3%2By7wO7X%2Bwwy%2FDqU%2FGA00%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=022c2d85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F977429739433373696&h=84a75eba\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/977429739433373696</a><br />\n<br />\n香港是一個沒有資本管制的國家，預期樓價升，資本就會流入，樓價就會升，預期樓價跌，資本就會撤，樓價就會崩。林鄭甚麼辣招都是無用的，因為不想樓價跌。而樓價跌、崩，又有另一些問題。所謂增加供應，只會不斷犧牲農地、停車場地、社區設施、綠化帶。白白犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/977434629505409024\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F977434629505409024&d=O3%2By7wO7X%2Bwwy%2FDqU%2FGA00%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=d9f3c2e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F977434629505409024&h=e0b2960e\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/977434629505409024</a><br />\n<br />\n當年麥督公營房屋十年建屋計劃一出，香港樓價是崩了，當然之後回復又升。對私樓樓價，已不能做更多事。狼英、林鄭，做的事都是無用的。以前英屬港府不會這樣玩的。香港是一個沒有資本管制的國家，在中國有用的做法，在香港是無用的。香港不是中國。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/977438994978844675\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F977438994978844675&d=O3%2By7wO7X%2Bwwy%2FDqU%2FGA00%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=6517c357\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F977438994978844675&h=676f995c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/977438994978844675</a><br />\n<br />\n年青一代面對的是沒有屬於自己個人的私人空間和睡眠空間，卻被說成置業問題。完全是狼英、林鄭置換論題。"},{"pid":"ef5e8f36d302743d66aabe63c158c445c4f35ef8","tid":605782,"uid":57513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T03:34:07.000Z","msg":"人口政策問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港人口增長超過100%係來自支那,日日150個點起都唔夠住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e3700fd6a740f365d1e734921f6ee132df5dd08","tid":605782,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef5e8f36d302743d66aabe63c158c445c4f35ef8","tid":605782,"uid":57513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T03:34:07.000Z","msg":"人口政策問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港人口增長超過100%係來自支那,日日150個點起都唔夠住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T16:01:40.000Z","msg":"其實由97開始已係日日150　如果係咁<br />\n１、佢地應該好有米　一齊令樓價飆升<br />\n２、97後樓價就應該冇冧過"}]}